About this item

  • Duracell 2032 lithium coin batteries are designed for use in keyfobs, small remotes, scales, wearables, sensors, medical devices (glucometers, digital thermometers), sports devices (heart rate monitor, bike accessories)
  • Duracell lithium coin batteries have child safety pack: Tamper-proof pack with double blister so that it is impossible for a child to open without scissors
  • Duracell 2032 lithium coin batteries up to 50 percent more power (vs key fob IEC standard test minimum average duration for CR2032 lithium coins results may vary by device and usage patterns)
  • Duracell 2032 lithium coin batteries use high-purity lithium
  • Guarantee for 10 years in storage with Duralock Power Preserve technology
  • Duracell lithium coin batteries are available in 1220, 1616, 1620, 1632, 2016, 2025, 2032, 2430 and 2450 sizes

Product Safety

This product is subject to specific safety warnings

  • Warning:Not suitable for children under 3 years. For use under adult supervision

From the manufacturer


Long lasting specialty, coin and button batteries

Duracell offers a wide range of specialty, button and coin batteries to power a wide range of devices, from electronics to medical devices and small toys.

Available sizes:

Lithum coins:

1220, 1616, 1620, 2016, 2025, 2032, 2430, 2450

Buttons:

LR43, LR44, LR54, 625A, 364, 377, 394, 301/386, 303/357, 361/362, 370/371, 384/392, 389/390, 395/399, 303/393

Specialty batteries:

28L, 1/3N, MN21, N, AAAA, J, MN11, MN27, 123, CR2, CRV3, 223, 245.

Features & Benefits

Long Lasting Power

The trusted Duracell quality is also available for all your coin, button and specialty batteries.

Easy to find right size

Quickly find the correct battery size for your device by checking the large battery size numbers on pack.

Duralock

Did you know that most batteries lose power over time, even when not in use? Duracell's DuralockTM technology preserves batteries power in storage before being used.

Lithium Coin Battery Safety

Keep batteries away from children. Warning sticker and engraved warning are included on batteries, as well as a double blister around the battery.

    Safety Information:

    Caution: battery can explode or leak if heated, disassembled, shorted, recharged, exposed to high temperature or inserted incorrectly. Do not mix used and new batteries, different brands or types. Keep away from children. Do not swallow. If swallowed, seek medical advice at once.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
